author: @viny12345678
text: I think you misconcieved what the purpose is of the titan v. The titan v is meant for deep-learning, not gaming, rendering or even mining. Of course you can these things, but it is not the main purpose of the titan v. It is also definitly not meant for  the average consumer, hence the steep price. And it is not even the most expensive GPU, I believe the Nvidia Quadro series are about twice the price of a titan v. But I DO think that you need/want one. I would even donate (this would even be my first donation ever)  to get you this card specificly, so you should definitly start some Kickstarter or Indiegogo project. Can't wait to see some major improvements for your AI's because of this card.
